\'\' color=\'\']\r\n<h1>Scrip Programs</h1>\r\nImagine being able to support Eastside Community School every time you buy groceries, go to the movies, or enjoy a cup of coffee. That’s the beauty of our Scrip Programs: simply sign up, shop and you’re supporting your school. Scrip Programs benefit us at no cost to you.\r\n[/av_textblock]\r\n\r\n[av_toggle_container initial=\'0\' mode=\'accordion\' sort=\'\']\r\n[av_toggle title=\'PCC Natural Markets\' tags=\'\']\r\nWholesome foods and the good feeling of supporting Eastside Community School. We receive 5% of the amount of your purchase at PCC Natural Markets when you use your PCC Scrip card or key tag to pay for your groceries. Purchase your card from the school office. The cost is applied to the card and can be used to pay for your next PCC purchase.\r\n\r\nFrequently Asked Questions:\r\n\r\n<strong>Q: Does it cost me anything?</strong>\r\n<strong>A:</strong> No. It does not cost you one penny more then you normally would spend on your groceries. The 5% donation comes from the store, out of their profits, not your pocket!\r\n\r\n<strong>Q: What\'s the catch?</strong>\r\n<strong>A:</strong> There is no catch!\r\n\r\n<strong>Q: How do I add money to my card?</strong>\r\n<strong>A:</strong> It\'s simple; you just add money to your card at any PCC store at the check stand. You can pay using VISA, MasterCard, Discover, debit cards or cash.\r\n\r\n<strong>Q: Does the card ever expire?</strong>\r\n<strong>A:</strong> No. The money you add to your card will stay on it until you spend it.\r\n\r\n<strong>Q: Can I check the balance on my card?</strong>\r\n<strong>A:</strong> Yes, you can check the balance on your card at any PCC check stand or by logging on to www.pccnaturalmarkets.com/scrip\r\n\r\n<strong>Q: What happens if the card is lost of stolen?</strong>\r\n<strong>A:</strong> If you loose your card let us know and we will have the any money left on the card transferred to a new card.\r\n[/av_toggle]\r\n[av_toggle title=\'Amazon Smile\' tags=\'\']\r\nAmazonSmile is a simple and automatic way for you to support Eastside Community School every time you shop, at no cost to you. When you shop at <a href=\"http://smile.amazon.com\" target=\"_blank\">smile.amazon.com</a>, you’ll find the exact same low prices, vast selection and convenient shopping experience as Amazon.com, with the added bonus that Amazon will donate a portion of the purchase price to our school. Setting up Eastside Community School to receive donations for your purchases is very easy. If you already have another non profit set up, changing it is simple as well. Here are the instructions:\r\n\r\nOn your first visit to AmazonSmile (<a href=\"http://smile.amazon.com/\" target=\"_blank\">smile.amazon.com</a>), you are prompted to select a charitable organization from our list of eligible organizations. You can change your selection at any time.\r\n\r\nTo change your charitable organization:\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Sign in to <a href=\"http://smile.amazon.com/\" target=\"_blank\">smile.amazon.com</a> on your desktop or mobile phone browser.</li>\r\n 	<li>From your desktop, go to Your Account from the navigation at the top of any page, and then select the option to Change your Charity. Or, from your mobile browser, select Change your Charity from the options at the bottom of the page.</li>\r\n 	<li>Select a new charitable organization to support. After you type in \"Eastside Community School,\" be sure to choose Eastside Community School in Bellevue, WA.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<div>If you are a Chrome user, you can install a plugin, <a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/smile-always/jgpmhnmjbhgkhpbgelalfpplebgfjmbf?hl=en\">Smile Always</a>, that will automatically redirect your browser to AmazonSmile when you type in amazon.com.\r\n\r\nFor more information about the AmazonSmile program, go to <a href=\"http://smile.amazon.com/about\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://smile.amazon.com/about&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1522381549156000&amp;usg=AFQjCNEW1Q69EReM3qRzcOWZDMwIpMx0kQ\">http://smile.amazon.com/<wbr />about</a>.</div>\r\n[/av_toggle]\r\n[av_toggle title=\'Safeway Club Card\' tags=\'\']\r\nEastside Community School Safeway Club Card registration is coming soon.\r\n\r\n<!--Register your Safeway card, and 1% of every shopping trip will go to support Three Cedars Waldorf School. <a href=\"http://www.safeway.com/ShopStores/Club-Card\" target=\"_blank\">More information.</a>-->\r\n[/av_toggle]\r\n[/av_toggle_container]\r\n\r\n'),(3647,3308,'layout',''),(3648,3308,'simplepagesidebars_page_sidebar_update_nonce','a6d575ef4e'),(3649,3308,'simplepagesidebars_page_sidebar_name','Support Us'),(3650,3308,'simplepagesidebars_page_sidebar_name_new',''),(3651,3308,'sidebar','Support Us'),(3652,3308,'header','yes'),(3653,3308,'footer',''),(3654,3308,'_edit_lock','1541139872:11'),(3656,3308,'_dp_original','3306'),(3657,3310,'_edit_last','6'),(3658,3310,'_wp_page_template','default'),(3659,3310,'_aviaLayoutBuilder_active',''),(3660,3310,'_aviaLayoutBuilderCleanData',''),(3661,3310,'layout',''),(3662,3310,'simplepagesidebars_page_sidebar_update_nonce','b4666467d0'),(3663,3310,'simplepagesidebars_page_sidebar_name','Support Us'),(3664,3310,'simplepagesidebars_page_sidebar_name_new',''),(3665,3310,'sidebar','Support Us'),(3666,3310,'header','yes'),(3667,3310,'footer',''),(3668,3310,'_edit_lock','1540872158:11'),(3670,3310,'_dp_original','3308'),(3671,3304,'_sidebar_name','Support Us'),(3748,3189,'_wp_attachment_image_alt','Young Children Help Fill the Sandbox'),(3747,3228,'_wp_attachment_image_alt',''),(3746,3342,'_edit_lock','1509839301:8'),(3745,3342,'_edit_last','2'),(3744,3226,'_wp_attachment_image_alt','Young Children Need Time Outdoors'),(3743,3340,'_wp_attachment_image_alt','Writing in Main Lesson Book'),(3684,3314,'_menu_item_type','post_type'),(3685,3314,'_menu_item_menu_item_parent','0'),(3686,3314,'_menu_item_object_id','3304'),(3687,3314,'