ve Big to Three Cedars on May 5</a></h1>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; padding-top: 0; margin-bottom: 30px; font-size: 110%; line-height: 1.7;\">When you donate to Three Cedars through the <a href=\"http://www.seattlefoundation.org/npos/Pages/ThreeCedarsWaldorfSchool.aspx?bv=nposearch\" target=\"_blank\">Seattle Foundation</a> website on Tuesday, May 5, Three Cedars will receive a percentage of a matching funds pool. The Seattle Foundation’s mission is to foster powerful and rewarding philanthropy to make King County a stronger, more vibrant community. All donations large or small will make a difference for our students. Thank you for your generous support! <a title=\"Give Big Details\" href=\"http://threecedarswaldorf.org/give-big-details/\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a> or go to the Seattle Foundation website and <a href=\"http://www.seattlefoundation.org/npos/Pages/ThreeCedarsWaldorfSchool.aspx?bv=nposearch\" target=\"_blank\">Give Big now!</a></p>\r\n[/av_textblock]\r\n[/av_two_third]\r\n\r\n[av_layerslider id=\'1\']\r\n\r\n[av_section color=\'main_color\' custom_bg=\'\' src=\'\' position=\'top left\' repeat=\'no-repeat\' attach=\'scroll\' padding=\'default\' shadow=\'shadow\']\r\n[av_hr class=\'default\' height=\'50\' shadow=\'no-shadow\' position=\'center\']\r\n\r\n[av_one_fourth first]\r\n\r\n[av_heading tag=\'h4\' padding=\'1\' heading=\'Early Childhood Program\' color=\'\' style=\'\' custom_font=\'\' size=\'\' subheading_active=\'\' subheading_size=\'\' custom_class=\'\']\r\n\r\n[av_textblock size=\'\' font_color=\'\' color=\'\']\r\nPreschool and Kindergarten programs for ages 2-1/2 to six are centered on purposeful activity and imaginative play to foster healthy intellectual, emotional, and physical development.\r\n<p class=\"small\"></p>\r\n[/av_textblock]\r\n\r\n[av_button label=\'Learn More\' link=\'page,2483\' link_target=\'\' color=\'theme-color\' custom_bg=\'#444444\' custom_font=\'#ffffff\' size=\'small\' position=\'left\' icon_select=\'no\' icon=\'25\']\r\n\r\n[/av_one_fourth][av_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[av_heading tag=\'h4\' padding=\'1\' heading=\'Elementary Grades 1-5\' color=\'\' style=\'\' custom_font=\'\' size=\'\' subheading_active=\'\' subheading_size=\'\' custom_class=\'\']\r\n\r\n[av_textblock size=\'\' font_color=\'\' color=\'\']\r\nEngaging, art-infused academics challenge students to develop a wide range of skills and capacities. Our rich curriculum is based on a profound understanding of human development, and inspires a life-long love of learning.\r\n[/av_textblock]\r\n\r\n[av_button label=\'Learn More\' link=\'page,2488\' link_target=\'\' color=\'theme-color\' custom_bg=\'#444444\' custom_font=\'#ffffff\' size=\'small\' position=\'left\' icon_select=\'no\' icon=\'25\']\r\n\r\n[/av_one_fourth][av_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[av_heading tag=\'h4\' padding=\'1\' heading=\'Middle School Grades 6-8\' color=\'\' style=\'\' custom_font=\'\' size=\'\' subheading_active=\'\' subheading_size=\'\' custom_class=\'\']\r\n\r\n[av_textblock size=\'\' font_color=\'\' color=\'\']\r\nOur curriculum is carefully designed to correspond with the interests and increased abilities of the middle school student, producing versatile, articulate, self-sufficient, inquisitive graduates, well prepared to continue their academic path.\r\n[/av_textblock]\r\n\r\n[av_button label=\'Learn More\' link=\'page,2488\' link_target=\'\' color=\'theme-color\' custom_bg=\'#444444\' custom_font=\'#ffffff\' size=\'small\' position=\'left\' icon_select=\'no\' icon=\'25\']\r\n\r\n[/av_one_fourth][av_one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[av_heading tag=\'h4\' padding=\'1\' heading=\'School Tour\' color=\'\' style=\'\' custom_font=\'\' size=\'\' subheading_active=\'\' subheading_size=\'\' custom_class=\'\']\r\n\r\n[av_textblock size=\'\' font_color=\'\' color=\'\']\r\n<strong>Wednesday, May 6, 2015</strong>\r\n\r\nVisit during school hours, view classes in session and ask your questions.\r\n<a title=\"Admissions : Open Houses & Tours\" href=\"/admissions-open-houses-t