eld similar celebrations for centuries, including pagan festivals in Germany during the Iron Age, the festival of Beltane of the Druids of the British Isles, and the festival of Flora during the Roman Empire. Regardless of its exact history, this ancient celebration connects us to the cycles of nature and life. We welcome spring and the return of light. We celebrate the magic of rebirth and awakening. The May Pole itself symbolizes the tree of life and the strength and vitality of nature; the garlands we weave metaphorically capture the magical power of nature lending us strength. Most importantly, May Faire is a joyful, colorful festival!\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://threecedarswaldorf.org/learn/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/May-Faire-2016-Flyer.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Flyer</a> <a href=\"http://threecedarswaldorf.org/contact-us/\" target=\"_blank\">Directions</a>\r\n[/av_textblock]\r\n\r\n'),(37222,8634,'_edit_lock','1460240179:2'),(37224,8633,'_wp_attachment_image_alt','May Faire crown'),(37257,8658,'_EventOrigin','events-calendar'),(37258,8658,'_edit_lock','1460412960:6'),(37259,8658,'_edit_last','6'),(37260,8658,'_EventShowMapLink','1'),(37261,8658,'_EventShowMap','1'),(37262,8658,'_EventStartDate','2016-05-05 18:30:00'),(37263,8658,'_EventEndDate','2016-05-05 20:30:00'),(37264,8658,'_EventStartDateUTC','2016-05-06 01:30:00'),(37265,8658,'_EventEndDateUTC','2016-05-06 03:30:00'),(37266,8658,'_EventDuration','7200'),(37267,8658,'_EventVenueID','7228'),(37268,8658,'_EventCurrencySymbol',''),(37269,8658,'_EventCurrencyPosition','prefix'),(37300,8658,'_EventCost',''),(37271,8658,'_EventURL',''),(37301,8658,'_EventOrganizerID','3400'),(37273,8658,'_EventTimezone','America/Los_Angeles'),(37274,8658,'_EventTimezoneAbbr','PDT'),(37275,8658,'_EventRecurrence','a:3:{s:5:\"rules\";a:0:{}s:10:\"exclusions\";a:0:{}s:11:\"description\";N;}'),(37276,8659,'_EventOrigin','events-calendar'),(37277,8659,'_edit_lock','1460406793:6'),(37278,8659,'_edit_last','6'),(37279,8659,'_EventShowMap