ions Team is here to help you through every step of the admissions process. Please do not hesitate to contact us at <a href=\"mailto:admissions@eastsidecommunityschool.org?subject=Admissions Inquiry\">admissions@eastsidecommunityschool.org</a> or (425) 598-2914.\r\n<h2>1. Submit an Inquiry</h2>\r\nSubmit an <a href=\"http://localhost:8888contact-us/\">online inquiry</a>, so we can send you information about our school and programs, and keep you informed about important admissions events and dates.\r\n<h2>2. Attend an Open House or School Tour</h2>\r\nCheck the dates and times of scheduled <a href=\"http://localhost:8888admissions-open-houses-tours/\">Open Houses and Tours</a>.\r\n\r\nIf you are not able to attend these scheduled events, we may be able to offer you an alternative date and time. Please <a href=\"http://localhost:8888contact-us/\">contact us</a> to schedule.\r\n<h2>3. Submit Application Form and Pay Application Fee</h2>\r\n<em><strong> FOR APPLICATION TO THE UPCOMING 2019-2020 SCHOOL YEAR</strong></em>\r\n\r\nClick <a href=\"https://mytads.com/a/eastside\">here</a> to begin your application in TADS, a web based system. This process will need to be done for each child you wish to enroll. Eastside Community School utilizes TADS for:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Applications</li>\r\n 	<li>Tuition &amp; Fees</li>\r\n 	<li>Registration</li>\r\n 	<li>Financial Aid</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<em><strong>\r\nFOR APPLICATION TO THE CURRENT 2018-2019 SCHOOL YEAR</strong></em>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Please complete the <a class=\"pdfFormDownload\" href=\"http://localhost:8888learn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Admission18-19_Application-Form.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Application Form</a>, and email it to <a href=\"mailto:admissions@eastsidecommunityschool.org?subject=Application\">admissions@eastsidecommunityschool.org</a>. This process will need to be done for each child you wish to enroll.</li>\r\n 	<li>Please pay the non-refundable Application Fee by Paypal or by check payable to <em>Eastside Community School</em>.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr valign=\"top\">\r\n<td><strong>Early Childhood and Grades 1-8</strong>\r\n\r\n<form action=\"https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr\" method=\"post\" target=\"_top\"><input name=\"cmd\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"_s-xclick\" />\r\n\r\n<input name=\"hosted_button_id\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"J4AZVRVBKMZVC\" />\r\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\"><input name=\"on0\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"“Application\" />Application Fee</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><select name=\"os0\">\r\n<option value=\"Application Fee\">Application Fee $75.00 USD</option>\r\n</select></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<input name=\"currency_code\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"USD\" />\r\n\r\n<input alt=\"PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!\" name=\"submit\" src=\"https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_paynowCC_LG.gif\" type=\"image\" />\r\n\r\n</form></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 50%;\"><strong>Parent &amp; Child</strong>\r\n\r\n<form action=\"https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr\" method=\"post\" target=\"_top\"><input name=\"cmd\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"_s-xclick\" />\r\n\r\n<input name=\"hosted_button_id\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"GY7P7ZRP4LQ9Y\" />\r\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><input name=\"on0\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"Tuition\" />Tuition</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><select name=\"os0\">\r\n<option value=\"Tuesday - Winter/Spring Session\">Tuesday - Winter/Spring Session $800.00 USD</option>\r\n<option value=\"Thursday - Winter/Spring Session\">Thursday - Winter/Spring Session $320.00 USD</option>\r\n</select></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<input name=\"currency_code\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"USD\" />\r\n\r\n<input alt=\"PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!\" name=\"submit\" src=\"https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_paynowCC_LG.gif\" type=\"image\" />\r\n\r\n</form></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h2>4. Request Teacher Questionnaire and Transcripts</h2>\r\nIf your child is currently attending another program, please submit:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://localhost:8888learn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Admission18-19_Admissions_Request-Records-Form.pdf\">Transcripts Request</a> (Grades 1-8 only)</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://localhost:8888learn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Admission18-19_TeacherEvaluation_G1-5.pdf\">Teacher Questionnaire (Grades 1-5)</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Teacher Questionnaire (Grades 6-8) [Downloadable form coming soon, please contact us for now.]</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<em>The Transcripts and Teacher Questionnaire must be submitted directly from the current school to Eastside Community School.</em>\r\n<h2>5. Family Interview with ECS Faculty</h2>\r\nOnce we have received your Application Form, Teacher Questionnaire, Transcripts (if applicable), and Application Fee, we will contact you for a Family Interview with faculty.\r\n<h2>6. Schedule a Visit (Grades Only)</h2>\r\nFollowing a successful Family Interview, eligible applicants to grades 2-8 will have an opportunity to schedule a visit (up to three days), and attend classes with their prospective teacher and peers.\r\n<h2>7. Acceptance</h2>\r\nAcceptance notifications will be emailed within one week of the Family Interview and/or visit. A completed Enrollment Packet, Enrollment Fee, and Tuition Deposit are due within 10 business days of the date on the Enrollment Agreement.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://get.adobe.com/reader/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Get Adobe Reader</a>\r\n\r\nTo use fill-able PDF forms, please save the form on your computer, and open in Adobe Reader.\r\n\r\n<!--In January 2016, Three Cedars Waldorf School merged with Seattle Waldorf School, and we have combined our admission process. To find more information about the application process for either campus, <a href=\"http://www.seattlewaldorf.org/admissions/application-process/\">please click here.</a>-->\r\n[/av_textblock]\r\n\r\n'),(39408,10262,'_wp_attached_file','2019/03/39223-Alma-Apostol.pdf'),(39285,9982,'classic-editor-remember','classic-editor'),(39286,9982,'_edit_last','11'),(39287,9982,'_avia_builder_shortcode_tree','a:14:{i:0;a:3:{s:3:\"tag\";s:12:\"av_textblock\";s:7:\"content\";a:0:{}s:5:\"index\";i:0;}i:1;a:3:{s:3:\"tag\";s:12:\"av_textblock\";s:7:\"content\";a:0:{}s:5:\"index\";i:1;}i:2;a:3:{s:3:\"tag\";s:8:\"av_table\";s:7:\"content\";a:0:{}s:5:\"index\";i:2;}i:3;a:3:{s:3:\"tag\";s:12:\"av_textblock\";s:7:\"content\";a:0:{}s:5:\"index\";i:3;}i:4;a:3:{s:3:\"tag\";s:8:\"av_table\";s:7:\"content\";a:0:{}s:5:\"index\";i:4;}i:5;a:3:{s:3:\"tag\";s:12:\"av_textblock\";s:7:\"content\";a:0:{}s:5:\"index\";i:5;}i:6;a:3:{s:3:\"tag\";s:8:\"av_table\";s:7:\"content\";a:0:{}s:5:\"index\";i:6;}i:7;a:3:{s:3:\"tag\";s:5:\"av_hr\";s:7:\"content\";a:0:{}s:5:\"index\";i:7;}i:8;a:3:{s:3:\"tag\";s:12:\"av_textblock\";s:7:\"content\";a:0:{}s:5:\"index\";i:8;}i:9;a:3:{s:3:\"tag\";s:8:\"av_table\";s:7:\"content\";a:0:{}s:5:\"index\";i:9;}i:10;a:3:{s:3:\"tag\";s:12:\"av_textblock\";s:7:\"content\";a:0:{}s:5:\"index\";i:10;}i:11;a:3:{s:3:\"tag\";s:8:\"av_table\";s:7:\"content\";a:0:{}s:5:\"index\";i:11;}i:12;a:3:{s:3:\"tag\";s:12:\"av_textblock\";s:7:\"content\";a:0:{}s:5:\"index\";i:12;}i:13;a:3:{s:3:\"tag\";s:12:\"av_textblock\";s:7:\"content\";a:0:{}s:5:\"index\";i:13;}}'),(39288,10196,'_menu_item_type','post_type'),(39289,10196,'_menu_item_menu_item_parent','10249'),(39290,10196,'_menu_item_object_id','9982'),(39291,10196,'_menu_item_object','page'),(39292,10196,'_menu_item_target',''),(39293,10196,'_menu_item_classes','a:1:{i:0;s:0:\"\";}'),(39263,10149,'layout',''),(39264,10149,'simplepagesidebars_page_sidebar_update_nonce','34ceb3230b'),(39265,10149,'simplepagesidebars_page_sidebar_name','Admissions'),(39266,10149,'simplepagesidebars_page_sidebar_name_new',''),(39267,10149,'sidebar','Admissions'),(39268,10149,'header','yes'),(39269,10149,'footer',''),(39270,